HTML: <div style="display:grid;gap:14px;padding:18px;border:1px solid #d8dee3;background:#fbfcfd;">
  <h2 style="margin:0;">Developer Dashboard is ready.</h2>
  <p style="margin:0;">Use <code>dashboard page new</code> and <code>dashboard page save</code> to create more pages.</p>
  <p style="margin:0;">Use <code>dashboard serve</code> to browse them and <code>dashboard collector run</code> to refresh prepared data.</p>
  <p style="margin:0;">Use <code>dashboard ps1</code> from your shell to render prompt status.</p>
</div>
